{"tid":1820332,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一位香港人對台灣人的感言","createTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T13:34:19.000Z","uid":239552,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a9ae168ca7f39af603d1961a85e8b90f1d4a493","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"今天，台灣人應感驕傲，你們在反共戰役中勝出一埸漂亮的一仗，今晚的結果為香港人打下強心針。你們用實際的行動演繹出「fight for Freedom, stand with Hong Kong」。但是，要有心理準備前路一定會困難重重，無論係經濟上，還是其他方面，都一定會有更大嘅阻礙，因為你們的對手是中共。在此，香港人送給你們的個人心法「不分化、不割蓆」。我相信台灣人的可塑性不比其他人弱，只要團結一心，未來一定會大鳴大放。最後，香港人一定會stand with Taiwan。"},{"pid":"8590887f53a38dec5277dff90d757788908f444d","tid":1820332,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d887c247cfd59f3c59aefc3eb9f28cd902ee48e9","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5f5f28fca0d45bb5a8922aea49ca1da596a8826b","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d887c247cfd59f3c59aefc3eb9f28cd902ee48e9","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d1e3dfb819d08e0058947955e3abb3e929652687","tid":1820332,"uid":210727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6c0ad021edcffc725ed820bce839333c44971f9","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f5f28fca0d45bb5a8922aea49ca1da596a8826b","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d887c247cfd59f3c59aefc3eb9f28cd902ee48e9","tid":1820332,"uid":239552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:48:50.000Z","msg":"